'''Praia Pesqueira''' is a seaside village in [[Caué District]] on [[São Tomé Island]] in [[São Tomé and Príncipe]]. Its population is 201 (2012 census).<ref name=census12>[https://www.ine.st/phocadownload/userupload/Documentos/DADOS%20LOCALIDADE%20PROJE%C3%87%C3%95ES/Publica%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20dos%20Resultados%20sobre%20Localidades%20-%20IV%20RGPH%202012.pdf 2012 detailed census São Tomé e Príncipe], [[Instituto Nacional de Estatística (São Tomé and Príncipe)|Instituto Nacional de Estatística]]</ref> The locality is located just south of [[Dona Augusta, São Tomé and Príncipe|Dona Augusta]] and 5 km southwest of [[São João dos Angolares]].
